strobo requires:
 - ffmpeg2theora
    On Debian, Ubuntu and other Debian-based distros:
    # aptitude install ffmpeg2theora
    On ArchLinux:
    # pacman -S ffmpeg2theora

 - oggz-tools
    Get it on: http://www.xiph.org/downloads/
    $ tar xfz liboggz-X.Y.Z.tar.gz
    $ cd liboggz-X.Y.Z.tar.gz
    $ ./configure
    $ make
    # make install
    OR:
    On ArchLinux:
    # yaourt -S aur/liboggz --> (Out of date!)

 - PIL (Python Imaging Library)
    # easy_install pil
    OR:
    Get it on: http://www.pythonware.com/products/pil/
    So, execute:
    $ tar xfz Imaging-X.Y.Z.tar.gz
    $ cd Imaging-X.Y.Z.tar.gz
    # python setup.py install
